						"async",
						"lookup"
					]
				},
				"description": "Async endpoint with query_text lookup.\n\nThis endpoint:\n1. Accepts only query_text (and optional query_file)\n2. Looks up the full query_data from the queries file\n3. Extracts limit, vector, alpha from query_data\n4. Executes parallel searches across 9 collections\n5. Returns aggregated results\n\nExample query_text values:\n- \"love and heartbreak\"\n- \"summer party vibes\"\n- \"feeling alone tonight\"\n- \"dance all night long\""
			},
			"response": []
		},
